                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><date>3<hi rend=\"sup\">rd</hi> Tishre\n                                                  5610</date>—</p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I avail myself of<lb/> an opportunity to request\n                                        you to forward<lb/> me at your earliest convenience a<lb/>\n                                        copy of Solomons Sermons (Goldsmiths<lb/> American edition)\n                                        for our mutual and amiable friend<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Miss David.</persName> If you send them to<lb/> me\n                                        I will hand them to her. Charge<lb/> them to me. I write\n                                        this in haste<lb/> at <persName>Dr David's</persName>. I\n                                        wrote you more<lb/> fully last week and hope you<lb/> have\n                                        received my letter. You might<lb/> send the Sermons,\n                                        suggests <persName>Miss D</persName>,<lb/> by <persName>Ms\n                                                  Joseph</persName>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Wishing you well over <add>כבוד</add><lb/> and\n                                                  many<add>?</add> years</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">I am dear Friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">yours truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">no occidents yet</hi>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34q7r93q/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
